#' Mathematically Rigorous Word-Level Edit Distance
#' @param text_a Character string representing the first document.
#' @param text_b Character string representing the second document.
#' @return A list containing the raw edit distance and the normalized similarity score.
# Developed by: Tatsuki Itagaki
# June 3, 2026 
